<section class="posts">
{% set postsCount = collections.posts | length %}
{% set latestPostsCount = postsCount | min(numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
{% set postslist = collections.posts | head(-1 * numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}
{% set postslistCounter = postsCount %}
{% include "postslist.njk" %}


</section>
<article class="intro">
<p>I am very lucky to be a husband to Mar, a father to Lucas and Nico, and a friend to Pancho <img src="/img/pancho.png" alt=pancho" class="pancho">. Find out more <a href="/about/">about me</a>.</p>
</article>



<h5>PROJECTS</h5>
<ul class="projects">
{%- for projects in collections.projects -%}
<li>
<h3><a href="{{projects.url}}">{{ projects.data.title }}</a> </h3> 
<img src="{{projects.data.cover}}" alt="cover image" class="cover"/> 
<p>{{ projects.data.excerpt | safe }}</p>
</li>

{%- endfor %}
</ul>

<article class="intro">
<p>Lately my <a href="/work/">work</a> and interest has revolved around data and data-decision making.</p>
</article>


<h5>TOPICS</h5>

<ul class="tagcloud">
{% for tag in collections | getKeys | filterTagList %}
{% set tagUrl %}/tag/{{ tag | slugify }}/{% endset %}
<li><a href="/tag/{{tag}}" >{{ tag }}</a></li>
{%- endfor -%}</ul>

